## 3. WEAPON MECHANICS DATA

### Acoustic & Kinetic Systems
* **Sonics (13):** Sequential waves; ignores physical shields.
* **Burst Sonics (39):** 3-wave intervals for disruption.
* **Machine Guns (05/06):** Scaling fire rates; high saturation.
* **Slug-Split Shotguns (33):** Heavy slugs apply **Slowdown**.

### Plasma & Radiation Systems
* **Radiation Guns (25):** 3-round bursts; +150% dmg on consecutive hits.
* **Auto-Rad Plasma (27):** +70% dmg (resets every 5 hits).
* **Auto-Burst Plasma (26):** Magnum (1), Taran (3), Redeemer (5) shot intervals.
* **Vacuum Cannons (38):** Life-leech plasma tethers. Links up to 4 targets at Lvl 4/5.

### Status & Tech Systems
* **Overheaters (01):** Unlimited ammo; accumulates heat/accuracy decay.
* **Corrosive (02/03/35):** Energy or Kinetic DOT effects.
* **Rust MGs (34):** Reduces target healing capability.
* **Lockdown (20/21/36):** Roots targets in place.
* **Lasers (28/29):** Continuous beams; Burnout (29) decays over time.
* **Freezers (04):** Beams that slow targets over time.

### Missile & Rocket Systems
* **Cluster Missiles (17/18):** Homing bursts (S.R. all at once / M.R. sequential).
* **Homing Rocket Launchers (30):** Applies **Fragility** stacks.
* **Incendiary/Grenades (19/32):** Apply **Blastcharge**; Grenades have 50m auto-aim.
* **Freezing Rockets (14/37):** C.R. is time-based; M.R. uses **Frostcharge** explosions.
* **Homing MGs (23):** Curved trajectory bullets.

### Specialty Ordinance
* **Harpoons (31):** Ignores all protection; grants **Myriad Aegis Shield**.
* **Shotguns (11/12/24):** High immediate DPS. Energy (11) locks down; Explosive (24) applies blastcharge.
* **Flamethrowers (09):** Ignores physical shields; massive Alpha damage.
* **Short Range Bonus (10):** Damage scales higher as distance decreases.

---

## 4. SIGNATURE ABILITY: "THE SWARM-SUIT"
Recalls active drones to form armor. Damage increases by **2% per total level** of the 10 active drones.

## 5. PASSIVE: RECYCLE PROTOCOL
When a drone is destroyed, remaining drones of that type receive a **Level Boost** (+1 Level for 30s). If maxed, gain **20% Fire Rate** instead.



